      "sortOrder": 1,
      "title": "Ambition Meets Industry",
      "body": "Your ambition statement is not abstract — it lives in a real market.\n\nToday you will:\n• Interview or observe a practitioner\n• Capture industry insights for your squad\n• Draft your opportunity reflection",
      "speakerNotes": "Show example connection: ambition → industry niche. 4 min.",
      "discussionQuestions": [
        "Read your ambition — what industry segment fits?"
      ],
      "imageUrl": "/content/segment-1/week-1/day-2/deck-02/slide-01.png"
    },
    {
